title: Dallas Cowboys, Russell Wilson, Baker Mayfield and the New England Patriots
itunes:title: Dallas Cowboys, Russell Wilson, Baker Mayfield and the New England Patriots
description:
Colin wonders where the Dallas Cowboys team who won yesterday has been all year. He explains why Russell Wilson should be MVP, why he feels Baker Mayfield just isn’t that good, why the Patriots will most likely be punished hard for their recent scandal, and why the Rams need to move on from Todd Gurley.

Guests include Michael Vick, Trent Dilfer, and James Harrison.
